{"tid":905272,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【唱淡樓市】曾俊華：樓市下行周期開始 加息2至3%部份人供不起樓","createTime":"2018-11-17T04:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T10:51:38.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"df8b64cd55dd0fb4108d8ca3565a5dc401fe249f","tid":905272,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:00:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【唱淡樓市】曾俊華：樓市下行周期開始 加息2至3%部份人供不起樓</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181116/58922750\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181116%2F58922750&d=uYzQBpRLOc79lpwGqeW%2Bx0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=9683fd06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181116%2F58922750&h=9e3ddb9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181116/58922750</a><br />\n<br />\n二手樓市持續出現劈價潮，市場對樓市睇法傾向悲觀，上月23日，前財政司司長曾俊華於公開場合說，樓價會否跟隨大市繼續向下調整，主要視乎市場心理，「通常價錢唔升，少啲人會買樓」，而且利息升都會有影響。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日曾俊華接受《彭博電視》訪問時講得更明確，稱低息環境、欠缺投資出路，導致過去十年本港樓市持續上升，「這並不尋常」，隨着借貸成本上升，會令樓市回復到更穩定的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n他又提到，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓市下行周期已經開始，若利率上調2至3%，部份人可能未能負擔供款</span>，籲港人需留意相關風險。</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，訪問亦提及聯滙，曾俊華指，過去30年不時出現檢討聯滙的聲音，他反問「香港作為細小型經濟體，可以與哪單一貨幣掛鈎呢？」他說無論是掛鈎單一貨幣，抑或改為掛一籃子貨幣，管理上都有困難，故應該繼續保持聯滙制度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沒事兒沒事兒"},{"pid":"bc37df6a5a911bc242a97e50245c04b47bc68aa7","tid":905272,"uid":161015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:04:54.000Z","msg":"點解有壓力測試 simulate 左加三厘先批按揭 宜家又話加三厘會有人斷供<br />\n媽呀 好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6b2c9b6b8d6217c8224a6536351fdb226f6ed7","tid":905272,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a340c94602a4c691fe81df5a0962d3199e696e31","tid":905272,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8887525accfadb45542064d65cc80f32e021fb2b","tid":905272,"uid":106247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc37df6a5a911bc242a97e50245c04b47bc68aa7","tid":905272,"uid":161015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:04:54.000Z","msg":"點解有壓力測試 simulate 左加三厘先批按揭 宜家又話加三厘會有人斷供<br />\n媽呀 好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:52:33.000Z","msg":"壓測測唔到個業主失業同減人工"},{"pid":"604f3237fb15695d3477fdd91e511a42acf58520","tid":905272,"uid":35941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:59:32.000Z","msg":"品客佬租租廢淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655ae5a06f81203a473142fb8948d1a04afe2d20","tid":905272,"uid":58618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc37df6a5a911bc242a97e50245c04b47bc68aa7","tid":905272,"uid":161015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:04:54.000Z","msg":"點解有壓力測試 simulate 左加三厘先批按揭 宜家又話加三厘會有人斷供<br />\n媽呀 好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"佢宜家話負擔唔到即<br />\n你人工減少少 物價唔加減 但每個月供多10%你都死啦<br />\n份糧唔係淨供樓架嘛 到時唔退稅一定仲慘"},{"pid":"4f12f4eae3061721aca01ddfd42445060bc4ff1b","tid":905272,"uid":92512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:40:03.000Z","msg":"咁樣嘅情況，都係因為佢之前做財爺比留比下一屆嘅屎。<br />\n<br />\n心捻，收皮啦，以為自己好幽默，當市民冇腦嘅。"},{"pid":"4f48bcd99f20f95e875d22ff38a109143750c953","tid":905272,"uid":73598,"like":2,"dis